OL,3,C'This drought is killing us': Sicilian
OL,4,Clocals left without running water
OL,6,FITV News Europe Editor James Mates met
OL,7,Fwith residents of the much-loved
OL,8,FItalian holiday destination in a
OL,9,Fsevere water crisis, who are facing
OL,10,Funcertain prospects for relief
OL,12,FIt's mid-October but a fiery Sicilian
OL,13,Fsun is still blasting the central
OL,14,Fpiazza in the town of Caltanissetta.
OL,16,FA severe water crisis is gripping the
OL,17,Fregion as the ongoing drought
OL,18,Fstretches into autumn.
