OL,3,C'This drought is killing us': Sicilian
OL,4,Clocals left without running water
OL,6,FProlonged dry conditions have
OL,7,Fdrastically reduced water reserves,
OL,8,Fleaving the city and surrounding areas
OL,9,Fon the brink of running out of water.
OL,11,FAs temperatures remain unseasonably
OL,12,Fhigh, local authorities are scrambling
OL,13,Fto implement emergency measures, while
OL,14,Fresidents face uncertain prospects for
OL,15,Frelief.
