OL,3,C'This drought is killing us': Sicilian
OL,4,Clocals left without running water
OL,6,FITV News spoke to local Patrizia
OL,7,FGelsomino, who shares a home with her
OL,8,Felderly mother and severely disabled
OL,9,Fson, and who has been without water
OL,10,Ffor over four months.
OL,12,F"This hot in October? Never, never,
OL,13,Fnever," she said.
OL,15,F"Last year was warm, but this year is
OL,16,Ftoo much. This drought is really
OL,17,Fkilling us."
OL,19,FUndrinkable water for washing and
OL,20,Ftoilets is delivered by lorry to a
OL,21,Fcistern in Ms Gelsomino's garden.
