OL,6,FThe family are still waiting for this
OL,7,Fweek's delivery, which costs them E150
OL,8,F(#125).
OL,10,FIt's a similar situation for business
OL,11,Fowners, with bakery Valentina Sfalanga
OL,12,Fforced to use expensive bottled water
OL,13,Fto make bread and pastries.
OL,15,FShe told ITV News the cost could force
OL,16,Fher to shut, and added: "I've been
OL,17,Ftold if I don't have water I'll have
OL,18,Fto close. The bank doesn't care that I
OL,19,Fdon't have water. It doesn't care that
OL,20,FI employ ten people."
